name: AmbientWaterfallSoundsforSleep
0:
”Alexa open ambient waterfall sounds”
”Alexa ask ambient waterfall sounds to play for 30 minutes”
”Alexa stop”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: ambient waterfall sounds
des: Let the sounds of an ambient waterfall raging outside thrust you into a deep sleep. Ambient Waterfall Sounds is the ultimate science-backed companion for relaxation, focus, and better sleep. \n\nAll you need to do is say Alexa start Ambient Waterfall Sounds, and she will play the track for 30 minutes. This is a perfect skill to leave on while you are asleep, to use for relaxation and meditation, or to tune in and focus on your work.
